Paper: hep-th/0112181

Date: 2001-12-19

Title: Projection on higher Landau levels and non-commutative geometry

Authors: Nicolas Macris, Stephane Ouvry

Comments: 12 pages, latex, corrected version

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A35 (2002) 4477-4484

The projection of a two dimensional planar system on the higher Landau levelsof an external magnetic field is formulated in the language of the noncommutative plane and leads to a new class of star products.